Some interesting concepts on networking and socket

Communication over internet

(user 1 )Application Layer-->Transport Layer-->Internet Layer-->Link Layer--[Ethernet]-->Link-->Internet-->Link-->Fiber-->Link-->Interner-->Link-->Ethernet--Link-->Internet--Transport--Application (user 2)


We can have communication between two transport layers and get the data from one application layer to another via python.

This connection is called socket

Ports are equivalent to extensions in a company. You can call company but to talk to specific person you need to dial extension. similary on network, you need to specify port to interact with certain application.


